A jQuery micro-library to define multiple dependencies and set callbacks which are called when they are reached.

See the simple example (simple_example.html) for a basic example.

See comments in jquery.waitfor.js for some more info.

Versions-
================================================
v0.1		A very simple example case using timers to show $.waitFor in use.
v0.1.1		Includes a new example for google maps. Fixed some bugs from previous release.
v0.1.2		Added new function for creating enclosed callback functions with multiple parameters $.waitForClosure